snippet.title: Hazelnut Hex - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Rescue breakfast in this action-packed arcade-style shoot 'em up! Hazelnut Hex is available now from itch.io and the Nintendo Switch eShop!

https://chunderfins.itch.io/hazelnut-hex
https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/hazelnut-hex-switch/

Soundtrack available at Bandcamp!
https://chunderfins.bandcamp.com/album/hazelnut-hex-ost

The cool bit near the end of the trailer where she shoots the big laser was animated by Liam Fantinatto!
https://twitter.com/lumpef
